				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Estra Stir is a gossip columnist for the Baldurs Mouth. She has a devilish artifact, the Eye ofTitivilus,  that allows her to detect the thoghts of the people she is talking too. She wants to pump the players for juicy personal details to print in her gossip column."
